locList.addLoc("hyperstorage_facility_desc","Hyperstorage facilities utilize cutting edge stasis and vacuum manipulation technologies to store materials.\n\nWhile these buildings produce some £minerals minerals for machine empires and food £food and minerals £minerals for organic empires, their main advantage appears when an empire suffers from a §RMineral Deficit§!, §REnergy Deficit§! or, in the case of organic empires, §RStarvation§!. When this occurs, the hyperstorage facility will begin to output large quantities of up to §Gtwo required resources§!.","en")

